HSCM Bermuda Fund Ltd.  Financing
HSCM Bermuda Fund Ltd. just submitted form D announcing  Indefinite equity financing.  This is a new filing. HSCM Bermuda Fund Ltd. was able to sell $91,595,000. The total private offering amount was Indefinite. The financing was made by 12 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $0. The financing document was filed on 2016-12-08. HSCM Bermuda Fund Ltd. is based in  ONE DOCK STREET, SUITE 404  STAMFORD 06902. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The form was signed by  Michael Millette.





