Scroll to read moreThought-leading, sector-focused investingHudson Structured Capital Management is an asset manager focused on alternative investments targeting mezzanine level returns. Our focus is on the Re/Insurance and Transportation sectors.Scroll to read moreThought-leading, sector-focused investingHudson Structured Capital Management is an asset manager focused on alternative investments targeting mezzanine level returns. Our focus is on the Re/Insurance and Transportation sectors.Scroll to read moreThought-leading, sector-focused investingHudson Structured Capital Management is an asset manager focused on alternative investments targeting mezzanine level returns. Our focus is on the Re/Insurance and Transportation sectors.Scroll to read moreThought-leading, sector-focused investingHudson Structured Capital Management is an asset manager focused on alternative investments targeting mezzanine level returns. Our focus is on the Re/Insurance and Transportation sectors.Scroll to read moreThought-leading, sector-focused investingHudson Structured Capital Management is an asset manager focused on alternative investments targeting mezzanine level returns. Our focus is on the Re/Insurance and Transportation sectors.








Our Focus
We focus on core economic sectors that are likely to outgrow global GDP, offer low correlations with broader markets and are experiencing a shift from balance sheet to market financing. Our team brings sourcing power, expertise and premier execution to private investing.
Our investing and advisory team is comprised of industry thought leaders. Significant investment and structuring experience position us to access and complete private market transactions. Our strategies are designed for investors looking for long-term consistent returns with mezzanine level risk. Our teams have over 115 years of re/insurance and 80 years of transport experience, and strong track records.






Our Founders
Michael MilletteMichael Millette was previously with Goldman Sachs for 21 years, 8 as a partner. Mr. Millette was a founder of Goldman’s Structured Insurance business and of its Reinsurance Principal business as well as Global Head of Structured Finance and Co-Chair of the Structured Finance Capital Committee. Before joining Goldman he was a portfolio manager at John Hancock.
David AndrewsDavid Andrews was formerly with PIMCO as Executive Vice President responsible for a multi-billion Transportation portfolio. Before joining PIMCO, Mr. Andrews was an Institutional Investor ranked analyst at UBS Securities covering Transportation and Industrials.






